            <h1 align="center"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><b><font size="6" face="Times New Roman, Times, serif"> Does High-Fructose Corn Syrup Have to Be in&nbsp;Everything?</font></b></font></h1>
            <p align="center"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><b><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif"> by <a href="mailto:rock.marathoner@gmail.com">Wilton D. Alston</a><br>
              <font size="1" color="#FFFFFF">by Wilton D. Alston</font></font></b></font></p>
            <p align="center"> <!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
              <script type="text/javascript">var addthis_pub = "egarris";</script>
              <a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onClick="return addthis_open(this, '', '[URL]', '[TITLE]')"><img src="http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/lg-share-en.gif" width="125" 
